
---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy" noIndex>
  <article class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-3xl flex-col gap-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <section class="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">How cookies are used</h2>
      <p>
        This site uses minimal cookies. Newsletter forms and the contact form rely on ConvertKit and Formspree cookies for security (anti-spam, rate limiting, confirmation). If Google Analytics is enabled, analytics cookies track anonymous traffic patterns.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Managing cookies</h2>
      <p>
        You can block or delete cookies through your browser settings. Third-party providers (ConvertKit, Formspree, Google) offer their own opt-out tools.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Questions</h2>
      <p>
        Contact <a class="text-emerald-600" href="mailto:contact@mparsonsauthor.com">contact@mparsonsauthor.com</a> for more information about cookie usage or data preferences.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
